data.description: Charming turn key country cottage set on a lovely quiet parcel in walking distance of the village of Philmont, a thoughtful community with lovely restaurants, a flourishing Co-op, and 4 minutes to the Hawthorne Valley School. Spacious, open floor plan, beautiful light, 2 bedrooms, large full bath and a clean, dry inviting basement. Centrally located with easy access to the Taconic Parkway, Harlemville, Chatham, Hillsdale and Hudson. Agent owned.
